## 2ï¸âƒ£ Must-Have Ranking Logic (Very Simple)

Search MVP ranking should be **rule-based**, not smart.

Priority order:

1. In-stock
2. Popular / fast-moving
3. Common pack sizes
4. Trusted brands
5. Price (only as a tie-breaker)

ðŸ“Œ No AI. No personalization.

---

## 3ï¸âƒ£ UX Expectations for Search MVP

Search results must:

- Load fast
- Be stable
- Be predictable

Each result should clearly show:

- Product image
- Name
- Size
- Price
- Add button

ðŸ“Œ User should add without opening PDP.

---

## 4ï¸âƒ£ MVP Metrics (Day-1 Tracking)

Search MVP must track:

- Search â†’ Add-to-Cart %
- Zero-result search rate
- Time to first add-to-cart
- Search usage per session

ðŸ“Œ If these are healthy, MVP is working.

---

## 5ï¸âƒ£ Explicitly NOT in Search MVP

This is **critical for scope control**.

âŒ Personalization

âŒ AI intent detection

