---

## 6ï¸âƒ£ Search MVP Success Definition

Search MVP is successful if:

- Users consistently find essentials in seconds
- Add-to-cart happens quickly
- Zero-result searches are rare
- Users trust search results

> Boring but reliable = success
> 

